Package Summary
Package
Description
de.feu.massim22.group3
The main package of the massim agent contest 2022 implementation of group 3 at Fernuni Hagen.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents
Provides classes, records and interfaces for implementation of agents which can compete in the massim agent contest 2022.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.belief
Provides classes for storing the belief of an agent about the current simulation.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.belief.reachable
Provides records for storing path finding information of a certain cell.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.desires
Provides classes which implement desires of an agent.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.desires.V2desires
 
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.events
Provides Enums which define event names.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.intention
Provides interfaces for modeling the intention of an agent.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.supervisor
Provides classes, records and interfaces for managing agent groups.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.V2utils
Provides utility classes and records for step processing of agents.
de.feu.massim22.group3.communication
Provides classes which manage the communication between agents and between agents and the simulation server.
de.feu.massim22.group3.map
Provides classes for storing information of the agent environment and for navigation in this environment.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils
Provides classes with helper methods and classes for debugging and logging.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger
Provides classes of a debugging tool to visualize the agent environment, the current state of the simulation and also data of the decision process of the agents.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData
Provides data classes to communicate between the main program and the debugger.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.logging
